How to Raise a Hero of the Pen


20 Sep 2020 14:30






Hello everyone! Veralta's here to present a tale of journalism, 'heroism', free speech, AIs, and virtual worlds, with a hint of a conspiracy within a conspiracy. This is one of the longest skips that I have written (clocking in at 4.9k when I last checked it), but somehow, I made it work.

This is also Part 1 of my team's series for the RenCon contest, where we plan to make the Foundation rumble with a brand-new GoI, Aviatica, which is made up of journalists. A massively secret force meets a massive truth-seeking and radical organization, in short.

Special thanks to basicskipreader for helping me figure out how to properly do the pacing, tension-building, characterization, motives of said characters, and ending of this article. You guys really helped me out making a story like this :)

As always, I hope you enjoy this piece!





